<p>Hello, <%= @target.email %>!</p>

<% if @self_initiated %>
  <p>You requested to step down from owner to admin in <strong><%= @organization.name %></strong>.</p>
<% else %>
  <p><strong><%= @initiator.email %></strong> requested to demote you from owner to admin in
  <strong><%= @organization.name %></strong>.</p>
<% end %>

<p>Your confirmation code is:</p>

<p style="font-size:28px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:4px"><%= @code %></p>

<p>Enter this code to confirm the change. It expires in 30 minutes.</p>

<p>If you didn't request this and don't want to be demoted, ignore this email - no change will
be made unless the code is confirmed.</p>
